# Additional setup for 4 vs 4

robot robot1 robot2 robot3 robot4
jc press 11 call Includes/PenaltyKickFirst # Shift+Ctrl+K (penalty kicK)
jc press 12 call Includes/PushingFreeKickFirst # Shift+Ctrl+L (fouL)

robot robot21 robot22 robot23 robot24
jc press 11 call Includes/PenaltyKickSecond # Shift+Ctrl+K (penalty kicK)
jc press 12 call Includes/PushingFreeKickSecond # Shift+Ctrl+L (fouL)

robot all
